{"tid":1049781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]潘杰霍紫泳威逼阿勇拍片自認成件事係網民兼蘋果老屈!!片中錯漏百出一齊睇!!","createTime":"2019-03-06T13:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T16:12:38.000Z","uid":35517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9ad780b74b71daf1c5f9078f3afd5b4f5e5828","tid":1049781,"uid":35517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEkLHVtynio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrEkLHVtynio&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=34346de4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEkLHVtynio</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/145119_5fe81018756b127cf6c03f2c9a93bb5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F145119_5fe81018756b127cf6c03f2c9a93bb5e.png&h=6cfe7ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/a2761ed255fccf160b8dd380e341f287.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fa2761ed255fccf160b8dd380e341f287.png&h=895430c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/1c7d5f083ea79f9fe80266ef472a97fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F1c7d5f083ea79f9fe80266ef472a97fe.png&h=636866d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.gyazo.com/8738836ecb8fc8f2cfbc5a8932ca01df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F8738836ecb8fc8f2cfbc5a8932ca01df.png&h=05a5709b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片中錯漏齊齊數：<br />\n1)背景為黃大仙(霍紫泳居住地區)<br />\n2)阿勇手持既稿 係印有霍紫泳中學既Notes紙<br />\n3)阿勇聲稱金額係比網民同蘋果失實誇大 但係佢親自承認40萬比霍紫泳敗哂(見圖)<br />\n4)阿勇話潘杰同霍紫泳冇呃佢, 但對話圖同信用卡圖, 清楚顯示阿勇係建基於想同霍紫泳結婚, 兼提供信用卡時有清楚講明 用得就代表霍紫泳應承, 而霍紫泳事後亦有用過, 但霍紫泳同時又係潘杰女朋友, 咁到底係霍紫泳一腳踏兩船, 定係阿勇明知人有男朋友都搞人條女? 仲要潘杰幫阿勇溝自己條女, 係有NTR傾向? 想知點兜<br />\n5)阿勇話見到人話霍紫泳係臭雞公廁好心痛 仲話想比人逼頭盡頭想自殺, 到底係潘杰霍紫泳逼你, 定係網民逼你, 你話比你話你傻鳩比人呃左50萬仲懵性性無哂臉想自殺都講得通, 而家竟然係一個呃你既人比人話臭雞所以好心痛兼想自殺, 呢part擺撚明就係條臭雞霍紫泳寫出嚟<br />\n<br />\n條片既錯漏多到不能盡錄 <br />\n潘杰霍紫泳真係當全香港人都係阿勇咁on99<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話 而家阿勇拍左片講唔追究 仲要咬番網民同蘋果一啖 唔洗再理佢<br />\n而家個情況就好似捉到個賣白粉嘅，唔係要白粉佬回水比道友，<br />\n而係令佢知道賣白粉係有問題<br />\n依家係佢比人捉正，仲要捉個道友出黎認係自己衰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/002651_ec87ed42a60f2040cd27c497423b8fcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F002651_ec87ed42a60f2040cd27c497423b8fcb.png&h=b874cd5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>潘杰你唔撚係諗住放完條片出嚟<br />\n一眾網民會話「連阿勇事主本人都出嚟澄清 睇嚟真係大家炒車怪錯左潘杰」吓嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母賤種仆街呃錢狗死全家啦 </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6bc6ea2c92cf60a07b5ad607e7b7c530eafda63b","tid":1049781,"uid":90697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc9ad780b74b71daf1c5f9078f3afd5b4f5e5828","tid":1049781,"uid":35517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEkLHVtynio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrEkLHVtynio&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=34346de4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rEkLHVtynio</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/145119_5fe81018756b127cf6c03f2c9a93bb5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fh